Myers- Highland Woods is located halfway between Naples and Fort Myers off of Route 41. Follow I-75 South to Corkscrew Road exit. Turn right and head west to U.S. Route 41. Turn left on U.S. 41 and travel approximately 7 miles to Highland Woods Blvd. Turn left and proceed to the left lane, visitors gate. From Naples- Follow I-75 North to Bonita Beach Road (Exit 116) and turn left. Travel to Route US 41(do not turn on old 41) and turn right (north). Turn right at the third traffic light (Highland Woods Blvd.) and proceed to the left lane at the gate.
